ShiKai Natural Everyday Shampoo - Imported (355 ml) Price: Rs.1800

ShiKai Natural Everyday Shampoo 12 fl oz (355 ml). Rich in Organic Ingredients. Extra Gentle Cleansing. Gently cleanses leaving hair soft and naturally shiny. The secret is nature s own natural soap-free cleanser. ShiKai Extract. For over 25 years we have used this very special botanical extract obtained from the fruit of an East Asian acacia tree. this extract provides rich dense natural lather that is gentle noticeably different and delivers beautiful shinyresults. Experience the difference for yourself. Our everyday shampoo is a simple mild formula designed for frequent use. Aloe Vera combined with a special Echinacea extract further enhances its mildness. Daily usage will neither strip the hair nor build up a residue. ShiKai has been developing natural skin and hair care products since 1975. Our goal is to make the finest most natural and safest products possible. to meet our high standards we formulate and produce each item with extreme care at our facilities in California. From Ingredients: full strength certified organic wildcrafted botanical organically grown and sustainably harvested. Made in USA
